"\">throttle configuration page</a> after having enabled the throttle module."
msgstr ""
"在啟用負荷模組後，必須在<a href=\"@throttle\">負荷設定頁面</a>裡啟用自動負荷"
"管制功能。"

#: modules/system/system.module:81
